How is it Verified?
VeriDate sends SMS code to phone number:

1. User clicks "Verify Phone" 
2. User enters phone number + country code
3. VeriDate validates format (E.164 format)
4. Twilio sends 6-digit SMS code
5. User enters code in UI
6. Code verified in real-time (10 minute TTL - shorter than email)
7. Webhook sent to dating app
8. Dating app stores: phone_verified = true
9. Badge appears on profile immediately

Technical:
├─ SMS delivery: Twilio (99.7% delivery in 30 seconds)
├─ Code generation: 6 digits (random, not sequential)
├─ TTL: 10 minutes (higher friction than email, stronger signal)
├─ Rate limiting: Max 3 attempts per number per hour
├─ Cost to VeriDate: \$0.03-0.05 per SMS (Twilio rates)
└─ Retry logic: Exponential backoff (1, 2, 4 minutes)
